<hymn_number>11131</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- btʿml ạ̹yh yạ yhwdẖạ kẖlạṣ htbyʿ
 nsyt ạlḥb dạ klh qrrt tḍyʿ
 wdạ klh ʿsẖạn ạ̹yh sẖwyẗ mlạlym
 dạ ḥbh fy qlbk fkr kẖlyk rḥym
 ạlqrạr- (ṭb ạ̉ṣbr ṭyb wạ̹ftkr zmạn
 ạ̹ftkr lmạ ạ̹kẖtạrk bạsmk ạ̹nt kmạn)2
 2- ạ̹stny̱ sẖwyẗ wạkẖdk ṭryqk ʿly̱ fyn
 ḥbk llmạl gẖwy̱ qlbk lyh tʿysẖ ḥzyn
 yạ kẖsạrẗ rkẖṣ ạlḥb qdạm ạltlạtyn
 dạ mạfysẖ fy ạldnyạ ysạwy ḥbh ạltẖmyn</lyrics>
<title>btʿml ạyh yạ yhwdẖạ !</title>
</song>